                        h2 Drift San José del Cabo: An Avant-Garde Boutique Sanctuary in the Art District
                        h3 The Cultural Heart of San José
                        p Drift San José del Cabo is a striking boutique retreat set in the vibrant pulse of the historic Gallery District. This is more than a hotel; it is an architectural expression of Baja, perfectly positioned to offer guests immediate pedestrian access to the cobblestone streets, artisan galleries, and world-class culinary scenes that define the soul of San José.
                        p Ideally located just 13 kilometers from Los Cabos International Airport (SJD), the property serves as an effortless arrival point for global nomads and culture seekers. From the iconic Thursday Art Walk to intimate mezcaleria experiences and hidden garden bistros, Drift places the most authentic facets of Baja directly at your doorstep.

        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 Curated Aesthetics and Authentic Baja Living
                        p Drift San José del Cabo is a celebration of minimalist design, raw natural textures, and localized craftsmanship. With 29 thoughtfully appointed rooms, the hotel fosters an intimate, socially-connected environment that stands in deliberate contrast to the traditional resort experience.

                        h3 Minimalist Accommodations
                        p Our rooms are designed as sanctuaries of light and texture, utilizing the colors and materials of the Baja landscape:
                        ul
                            li Artisan-crafted bedding featuring premium linens for ultimate comfort
                            li Minimalist, clean-lined interiors highlighting local woodwork and stone
                            li Private bathrooms with modern, earth-toned fixtures
                            li High-speed Wi-Fi designed for digital connectivity in a creative space

                        h3 The Drift Experience: A Social and Cultural Hub
                        p We cultivate an atmosphere where culture, gastronomy, and leisure converge:
                        ul
                            li The Courtyard Oasis: A central social space featuring a serene pool, hammocks, and palm-shaded lounges
                            li Drift Kitchen + Mezcal Bar: A sophisticated culinary destination specializing in regionally inspired menus and artisanal mezcal craft cocktails
                            li Active Baja Lifestyle: Complimentary access to premium yoga gear and high-performance surf equipment, encouraging connection with the local coastline
                            li Curated Community Programming: Exclusive events including backyard taco sessions, live acoustic performances, and seasonal mezcal tastings

                        h3 Cultural Immersion as a Lifestyle
                        p At Drift, we prioritize authentic local discovery over traditional resort entertainment. We invite our guests to integrate into the rhythm of the Gallery District, explore the latest gallery openings, and engage with the community’s vibrant creative spirit.

                        h3 The Definitive Boutique Escape
                        p Drift San José del Cabo appeals to the discerning traveler who values thoughtful design, deep cultural connection, and an atmosphere that is as lively as it is serene. By stripping away the superfluous, we offer a memorable, design-forward experience that captures the true, beating heart of Los Cabos.

